{"tid":1101632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被男友嫌是「臭西」 年輕女生狂洗下體反而更臭","createTime":"2019-04-11T07:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T07:44:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aa82cdc599f33a654949cd84726a27b94a0a2427","tid":1101632,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"1名年僅20多歲的女性初次與男友發生性關係時，卻被男友嫌棄下體味道「異於常人」，私下還與朋友笑她是「臭鮑魚」，讓她不知所措，狂洗下體，希望能去除異味，反而造成感染，讓味道更重。<br />\n <br />\n開業婦產科醫師陳思宇表示，女生也常因為生理期，下體悶了一整天有異味，會使用清潔力較強的陰道盥洗用品，或用去汙力強的鹼性清潔用品清洗。這些過多的動作，反而可能導致私密處發癢、發炎、產生更多異味。<br />\n <br />\n她曾收治一名患者每次那個來的時候，下體悶癢難耐且飄出異味，誤以為是洗得不夠乾淨才會癢，每次洗澡時都加強搓洗力道，並使用去汙力強的鹼性沐浴乳。長期下來，不僅搔癢狀況未改善，反而併發發炎感染，經就醫症狀才緩解。<br />\n <br />\n陳思宇提醒，女性如遇私密處搔癢症狀，先別急著把它「洗得很乾淨」，錯誤且過度的清潔可能導致私密處更癢、產生更多異味。<br />\n <br />\n陳思宇說，常見的錯誤清洗方式，像是清洗的力道加倍、時間加倍、頻率加倍或是會深度清潔陰道。還有女性為求清潔，會直接把手指伸進私密部位清洗，另外會選購強調有香味、美白等效果的盥洗用品來清洗下體。<br />\n <br />\n這些行為都會增加對於肌膚的刺激，建議應該要減少對於肌膚的刺激，避免購買強調美白、抗老訴求的產品，也不要深入清洗陰道，也別太用力，減少皮膚受損、酸鹼值被破壞的風險，清洗時間也不需特地拉長，選擇溫和保濕又能輕鬆沖洗的產品，就能達到清潔效果。"},{"pid":"9e4e4490b4831b48967b1f048eb8e872e6d0b020","tid":1101632,"uid":18569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"正宗臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3042a66d0f2d6d3a839d0ef303972abc316e5f","tid":1101632,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b4d718c6f4a289e8f1ea34ae299dd33a2aa6930","tid":1101632,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c3042a66d0f2d6d3a839d0ef303972abc316e5f","tid":1101632,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正解"},{"pid":"54f9327f29bf77970e30ed7f87e75fcdc31b510b","tid":1101632,"uid":28695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd6e2df40aab43b8a4f2471e3401bef514507b1","tid":1101632,"uid":157439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5b4d718c6f4a289e8f1ea34ae299dd33a2aa6930","tid":1101632,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c3042a66d0f2d6d3a839d0ef303972abc316e5f","tid":1101632,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:23:30.000Z","msg":"成車靜晒，司機減速"},{"pid":"15b93062426e13e63ac308b0a98eba9876529aa5","tid":1101632,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:31:46.000Z","msg":"臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9d1eddcf46fd46c6f6205da12d6bac7bf73bf2","tid":1101632,"uid":158472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"食得菇菌類多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食多d波羅就變香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553281438039440fdeaa0c61f7d3587c1a6ea7e0","tid":1101632,"uid":128111,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"個男人都幾仆街，食左人地隻豬仲要笑人臭閪，鬼唔望佢陽痿生梅毒生花柳"},{"pid":"e7a3d964022585da37b506e5b35a8ad70e5fe64e","tid":1101632,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"9成係念珠西啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"